    "# 1.3\n",
    "\n",
    "## Find most correlated features (at the 3 levels)\n",
    "\n",
    "The idea is to follow as done in lab 5:\n",
    "\n",
    "<ol>\n",
    "    <li> Scale the data \n",
    "    <li> Draw the Corr matrix \n",
    "    <li> Explain that highly correlated feats can be suppressed from the analysis \n",
    "<ol>\n"
   ]
